message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper is about music source separation, which is a subfield of audio signal processing. Other likely categories could include cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper discusses deep learning approaches, cs.SI (sound and music computing) as it is related to music signal analysis, cs.MM (multimedia) as it deals with audio and music data, and cs.IR (information retrieval) as source separation can be seen as a form of information retrieval from audio signals.
